<div class="page-content">
  <div class="page-intro">
    <p>A performing artist for nearly 20 years, I had the good fortune to play music across the US in a range of settings — from the Austin club circuit to international jazz festivals. I'm no longer performing actively, but the music lives on.</p>

    <p>A recipient of <a href="http://berklee.edu">Berklee College of Music</a>'s 1999 North American Scholarship Tour Award, I attended the prestigious college and graduated with my Bachelor of Music in 2001. I spent the years that followed teaching, touring, and performing alongside Austin's vibrant music community.</p>
  </div>

