  <section class="music-section">
    <h2 class="music-section-heading">Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-list">
      <div class="project">
        <h3 class="project-name">Mount Pressmore</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">An Austin-based group whose debut album was released in December 2013 and received press from around the country. We spent several years playing shows locally and recording.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <h3 class="project-name">ETC (Erik Telford Collective)</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">Trumpeter Erik Telford's ensemble, with whom I performed and recorded the album <em>Kinetic</em> (2010). The album received strong national press including selection as one of the Boston Globe's Top 10 Jazz Albums of 2010 and a JazzTimes top 40 nomination, leading to performances at the Rochester International Jazz Festival and the Monterey Jazz Festival.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <h3 class="project-name">The Susan Arbuckle Band</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">Austin singer-songwriter Susan Arbuckle's band, performing a mix of originals and soulful covers at venues including Antone's and Maverick's.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <h3 class="project-name">Champagne with Friends</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">A project with singer-songwriter Thomas Champagne, with whom I toured the central US. Equal parts road trip and recording session.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <h3 class="project-name">About:Blank</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">A jazz-funk-ska group I co-founded in Austin in 2005. About:Blank became a staple of the local music scene and was voted the #4 Jazz Band in Austin by the Austin Chronicle Music Awards in 2009–2010.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

